  "texts": [
    "Macro-Recall for MMSE (or CDR) is the average (at the note level) of the percentage of the MMSE items in the ground truth that are extracted by the LLM.",
    "Micro-precision is calculated as percentage of correct MMSE (or CDR) items extracted by the LLM, from among all extracted MMSE (or CDR) items by that LLM, and is calculated as one number across all notes combining all notes' entries.",
    "Micro-recall is similarly calculated as the percentage of all MMSE (or CDR) items mentioned in the ground truth that were extracted by the LLM.",
    "ChatGPT analyzed 765 notes for extraction of Mini Mental Status Exam (MMSE) and Cognitive Dementia Rating (CDR) scores and exam dates.",
    "Of these, 23 encountered API error (3%), and 20 were used to fine-tune prompt and hyper-parameters."
  ],
